as QA\n  participant "RegistrationFormInterface" as RFI\nend box\n\n== Main Flow: Register Patient with Symptoms ==\n\nRC -> RFI : displayRegistrationForm() : void\nnote right: [HTTPS] 
[authenticated] [encrypted in transit]\n\nRFI --> RC : submitPatientData(name: String, symptoms: List<String>) : void\n\nRC -> RS : registerPatient(patientData: PatientDTO) : Patient\nnote 
right: Authorization check: Triage_Nurse_Team must have Write permission\n\nRS -> RS : validatePatientData(patientData: PatientDTO) : boolean\nnote right: Must complete within 30 seconds\n\nalt 
Validation fails\n  RS --> RC : return ValidationError("Invalid patient data")\n  RC -> RFI : displayError("Please correct the input errors")\nelse Validation passes\n  RS -> P : 
createPatient(name: String, symptoms: List<String>) : Patient\n  note right: Patient record created with or without symptoms\n  \n  P -> RST : setState(RecordState.ACTIVE) : void\n  note right: 
State transition: null -> ACTIVE\n  \n  RS -> DB : savePatient(patient: Patient) : Patient\n  note right: [encrypted at rest] [authenticated]\n  \n  DB --> RS : return savedPatient\n  \n  RS -> 
SL : evaluateSeverity(symptoms: List<String>) : SeverityLevel\n  note right: Based on symptom severity algorithm\n  \n  RS -> PQ : addToQueue(patient: Patient, severity: SeverityLevel) : int\n  
note right: Queue position determined by severity\n  \n  PQ -> PQ : calculatePosition(severity: SeverityLevel) : int\n  \n  RS -> QA : enqueuePatient(queueEntry: QueueEntry) : boolean\n  note 
right: [TLS] [authenticated]\n  \n  QA --> RS : return success\n  \n  alt Immediate action required (SeverityLevel.CRITICAL or SeverityLevel.EMERGENCY)\n    RS -> NS : sendAlert(patient: 
Patient, severity: SeverityLevel) : void\n    note right: Notify medical staff of immediate action required\n    \n    NS -> NS : notifyMedicalStaff(patientId: String) : void\n    \n    NS --> 
RS : return\n  end\n  
